room_title: Escape room "Trouble in Tinseltown" by Lokey's Escape Rooms in Sarasota
room_description: Extra Extra: Startlet Slain on Sunset Strip. Listen up, Gumshoe: Hollywoodland is a dark place. The Boulevard chews them up and spits them out. So enter the suspect’s office, and get justice for the deceased. And by the way: There’s no need to adjust the color. This is the hardboiled 1940s, Flatfoot. You’d better get used to it.
